ygData.messageBody:
I think I saw Justene in Nexus.  I remember because my 17 yr old loves a girl named Justene and she doesn't think about him, "That Way."
 
I have a bard level 5 named Winday.  I am finding bardhood challenging.   My sons play on Prex and Karana.  They are not as nice on Karana.
